NAME
    App::SQLiteCounterSimpleUtils - CLI utilities for
    SQLite::Counter::Simple

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.002 of App::SQLiteCounterSimpleUtils
    (from Perl distribution App-SQLiteCounterSimpleUtils), released on
    2021-06-22.

DESCRIPTION
    This distribution provides the following command-line utilities:

    *   dump-sqlite-counters

    *   get-sqlite-counter

    *   increment-sqlite-counter

    which are basically CLI front-end for the functions in
    SQLite::Counter::Simple.

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/App-SQLiteCounterSimpleUtils>.

SOURCE
    Source repository is at
    <https://github.com/perlancar/perl-App-SQLiteCounterSimpleUtils>.

BUGS
